    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential emptiness and a sense of being a \"shell\" of their former self, questioning how to fix a perceived loss of soul or identity. The assistant responds with empathy, reframing the feeling as a potential protective mechanism and strongly recommending professional mental health support.",
